NAVTEX N/W NR: 43754/17
NOTICE TO ALL MARINERS
ON 3 JULY 2017 A TURKISH FLAGGED
MERCHANT VESSEL WAS FIRED UPON BY A
GREEK COAST GUARD BOAT. TURKISH
FLAGGED VESSELS SAILING IN THE AEGEAN
ARE REQUESTED TO BE VIGILANT AGAINST
SUCH INCIDENTS WITH RESPECT TO SAFETY
OF LIFE AND SAFETY ON NAVIGATION AND
SHOULD THERE BE A NEED THEY ARE URGED
TO SWIFTLY INFORM THE TURKISH COAST
GUARD AND TURKISH NAVY.
